      <title>美国在计划中的加沙停火谈判前加强中东军事力量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-bolsters-middle-east-forces-ahead-of-planned-gaza-truce-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在本周晚些时候恢复加沙停火谈判之前，美国加强了在中东的海军和空军力量，以帮助以色列抵御来自伊朗的任何大规模袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-bolsters-middle-east-forces-ahead-of-planned-gaza-truce-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
