      <title>拜登努力减轻消费者的客户服务障碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/biden-effort-aims-to-ease-customer-service-hurdles-for-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登的政府正在向美国人征求意见，以缓解他们在取消订阅或获得退款时面临的消费者服务障碍——这是在选举前解决选民厨房问题的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/biden-effort-aims-to-ease-customer-service-hurdles-for-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
