      <title>坦桑尼亚警方拘留反对派领导人，禁止青年集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/tanzanian-police-detain-opposition-leaders-ban-youth-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坦桑尼亚当局在周一举行的纪念国际青年日集会之前拘留了反对派领导人，并坚称逮捕他们是必要的，以降低暴力抗议的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/tanzanian-police-detain-opposition-leaders-ban-youth-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 07:46:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾抗议中国在领空采取“危险”行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/philippines-says-to-protest-china-s-dangerous-move-in-airspace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾表示将抗议中国空军在有争议的南海上空采取“危险”行动，这导致两国之间的紧张局势再次升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/philippines-says-to-protest-china-s-dangerous-move-in-airspace</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 05:18:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港最高法院维持黎智英抗议罪名判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/hong-kong-top-court-upholds-jimmy-lai-s-protest-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港最高法院维持对前传媒大亨黎智英因参加被禁的民主抗议活动而定罪的判决。此举正值香港司法系统因一系列外籍法官离职而面临越来越严格的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/hong-kong-top-court-upholds-jimmy-lai-s-protest-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 04:11:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
